e%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20to%20stop%20engaging%20with%20social%20media%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226380%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angel%20Reese.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9877ca98bc8fdc096dc8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224785%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAngel%20Reese%20says%20she%20is%20protecting%20her%20peace%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Alejandro%2FFIBA%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWNBA%20star%20Angel%20Reese%2C%2023%2C%20says%20she%20no%20longer%20lets%20social%20media%20comments%20get%20to%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BYears%20prior%2C%20I%20would%20comment%20back%20at%20things%20and%20let%20things%20continue%20to%20bother%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20she%20avoids%20engaging%20and%20focuses%20on%20the%20small%2C%20everyday%20moments%20that%20bring%20her%20joy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWNBA%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangel-reese-double-standards-celebrations-trash-talk-lsu-national-championship-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAngel%20Reese%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2023%2C%20is%20drawing%20a%20clear%20line%20between%20reel%20life%20and%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday's%20episode%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcxSH74qD3_M%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIMO%26quot%3B%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Reese%20said%20she's%20finally%20learned%20to%20protect%20her%20peace%20by%20tuning%20out%20what%20people%20say%20about%20her%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20tried%20to%20have%20some%20type%20of%20normalization%2C%20of%20knowing%20where%20I've%20come%20from.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20that.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20ever%20feel%20like%20I'm%20bigger%20than%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Reese%20told%20podcast%20hosts%20Michelle%20Obama%20and%20Craig%20Robinson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReese%20said%20she%20tries%20to%20practice%20gratitude%20every%20day%20and%20finds%20joy%20in%20the%20small%20things%2C%20like%20spending%20time%20with%20her%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20being%20able%20just%20to%20come%20home%20and%20turn%20my%20phone%20off%2C%20and%20just%20relax%2C%20and%20do%20the%20things%20that%20I%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she's%20gotten%20older%2C%20she's%20come%20to%20see%20social%20media%20as%20a%20distorted%20version%20of%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20over%20the%20years%20it's%20been%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20realize%20that%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20maturity%20of%20just%20understanding%20like%2C%20social%20media%20isn't%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20Reese%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20get%20so%20caught%20up%20in%20that.%20Years%20prior%2C%20I%20would%20comment%20back%20at%20things%20and%20let%20things%20continue%20to%20bother%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20no%20longer%20tries%20to%20engage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20rise%20to%20fame%20and%20the%20public%20scrutiny%20that%20followed%2C%20Reese%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangel-reese-highlights-unfairness-toward-black-women-in-sports-expert-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20way%20she%20was%20treated%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20neither%20normal%20nor%20acceptable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20part%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bnew%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20experience%20has%20made%20her%20more%20appreciative%20of%20the%20things%20she%20still%20has%20control%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReese%20has%20previously%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20negative%20attention%20she%20received%20online%20as%20her%20profile%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyF1NBEil-K4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20ESPN%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20cyberbullying%20after%20winning%20the%20NCAA%20Women's%20Basketball%20National%20Championship%20with%20Louisiana%20State%20University%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20had%20seen%20negativity%20like%20that%20on%20social%20media.%20I've%20had%20a%20huge%20following%20before%2C%20but%20it%20skyrocketed%20to%20millions%2C%20and%20it%20was%20bigger%20than%20basketball%2C%20when%20they%20were%20finding%20my%20address%2C%20my%20car%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20change%20my%20whole%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20Reese%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReese%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20rethinking%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-winslet-daughter-mia-threapleton-gen-z-no-social-media-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMia%20Threapleton%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20her%20mother%2C%20Kate%20Winslet%2C%20encouraged%20her%20to%20make%20a%20list%20of%20pros%20and%20cons%20for%20joining%20Instagram%20when%20she%20was%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cons%20completely%20outweighed%20the%20pros%20for%20me.%20That%20was%20quite%20a%20clarifying%20moment.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20more%20time%20I%20spend%20in%20this%20world%2C%20the%20more%20I'm%20really%20happy%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Threapleton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20biohacker%20and%20tech%20entrepreneur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-ai-agent-filter-social-media-feed-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBryan%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he's%20been%20doing%20social%20media%20%26quot%3Bfasts%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20health%20and%20wants%20an%20AI%20agent%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20buffer%20between%20him%20and%20his%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20want%20to%20see%20the%20raw%20feed.%20I%20want%20an%20AI%20agent%20to%20read%20it%20for%20me%2C%20strip%20the%20engagement%20metrics%20that%20hijack%20my%20judgment%2C%20filte