0%2Fqk8r9le4_donald-trump-afp_625x300_30_October_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-assesses-nato-allies-with-naughty-and-nice-list-amid-iran-war-11394757%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22White%20House%20plans%20a%20tiered%20NATO%20ranking%20based%20on%20defence%20support%20and%20cooperation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-assesses-nato-allies-with-naughty-and-nice-list-amid-iran-war-11394757%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-assesses-nato-allies-with-naughty-and-nice-list-amid-iran-war-11394757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-assesses-nato-allies-with-naughty-and-nice-list-amid-iran-war-11394757%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russians%20turned%20a%20recon%20drone%20into%20an%20extended-range%20mothership%20for%20its%20FPV%20quadcopters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20soldier%20holds%20an%20Orlan-10.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e991943fecbb42897a3075%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20troops%20use%20the%20Orlan-10%20primarily%20as%20a%20reconnaissance%20drone%2C%20but%20it%20was%20recently%20seen%20carrying%20FPV%20quadcopters%20under%20its%20wings.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20%2F%20Handout%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20was%20spotted%20using%20an%20Orlan-10%20to%20transport%20FPV%20drones%20under%20its%20wings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20previously%20used%20loitering%20munitions%20to%20carry%20drones%2C%20but%20is%20now%20using%20a%20reconnaissance%20system.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Orlan-10%20has%20a%20range%20of%20about%2074%20miles%2C%20which%20could%20greatly%20extend%20the%20range%20of%20an%20FPV%20strike.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Russian%20medium-range%20reconnaissance%20drone%20was%20recently%20spotted%20on%20the%20battlefield%20with%20first-person-view%20quadcopters%20mounted%20under%20its%20wings%2C%20making%20the%20system%20a%20flying%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhii%20%26quot%3BFlash%26quot%3B%20Beskrestnov%2C%20a%20drone%20advisor%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20defense%20ministry%2C%20posted%20two%20images%20of%20the%20fixed-wing%20system%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-keeps-orlan10-drone-flying-over-ukraine-with-western-parts-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOrlan%20drone%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20Telegram%20post%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%20Orlan%20got%20on%20camera.%20He%20has%20already%20dropped%20one%20FPV%2C%26quot%3B%20Beskrestnov%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F23%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBeskrestnov%20said%20that%20Russia%20was%20spotted%20before%20using%20loitering%20munitions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20delta-wing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shot-down-shahed-drones-helping-middle-east-zelenskyy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShahed%20exploding%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Gerbera%20decoy%20drone%2C%20to%20carry%20FPV%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20those%20drones%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Orlan%20is%20a%20reusable%20platform.%20The%20Orlan-10%2C%20a%20commonly%20used%20version%20of%20the%20recon%20drone%2C%20has%20an%20operational%20range%20of%20about%2074%20miles%2C%20though%20it%20can%20be%20preprogrammed%20to%20fly%20up%20to%20370%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20fixed-wing%20drone%20as%20both%20a%20carrier%20and%20signal%20relay%20could%20allow%20the%20pilot%20to%20significantly%20extend%20the%20reach%20of%20tactical%20quadcopters%2C%20which%20have%20been%20recorded%20hitting%20targets%20at%20a%20maximum%20distance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-drones-relay-system-long-range-milestone-donetsk-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eabout%2040%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20yet%20another%20battlefield%20innovation%20that%20continues%20to%20see%20troops%20push%20and%20merge%20simpler%20technologies%20for%20better%20effect.%20Ukraine%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20also%20experimented%20with%20relay%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20quadcopters%20or%20fixed-wing%20drones%20that%20extend%20another%20drone's%20signal%20range%20%E2%80%94%20for%20deep%20FPV%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20November%20that%20Russia%20was%20using%20Molniyas%2C%20fixed-wing%20loitering%20munitions%2C%20as%20carriers%20for%20FPV%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20tactic%2C%20however%2C%20is%20still%20emerging.%20Beskrestnov%20said%20Russia%20still%20hasn't%20been%20deploying%20FPV%20drones%20consistently%20from%20its%20Shaheds%20and%20Gerberas%2C%20which%20it%20produces%20thousands%20for%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20my%20observations%2C%20this%20technique%20has%20not%20been%20widely%20used%20by%20the%20enemy%20for%20a%20number%20of%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20Beskrestnov%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-turn-recon-drone-orlan-mothership-fpv-quadcopters-flash-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776917675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e993833fecbb42897a3077%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-turn-recon-drone-orlan-mothership-fpv-quadcopters-flash-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20used%20loitering%20munitions%20as%20drone%20carriers%20before%2C%20but%20this%20time%20used%20an%20Orlan-10%20recon%20drone%2C%20which%20has%20a%20range%20of%20about%2074%20miles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-turn-recon-drone-orlan-mothership-fpv-quadcopters-flash-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sorry%20to%20owners%20of%20older%20Teslas%20%E2%80%94%20your%20car%20won't%20be%20fully%20autonomous%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20registrations%20fell%20in%20California.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b4e0ab955b01c3294ce42d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20Tesla's%20older%20cars%20don't%20have%20fully%20autonomous%20driving%20capabilities.%3Cp%3ENewsday%20LLC%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20made%20several%20promises%20over%20the%20years%20that%20the%20Teslas%20people%20buy%20will%20be%20fully%20autonomous.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETurns%20out%20there's%20now%20a%20cut-off%20for%20how%20old%20the%20Teslas%20can%20be%20for%20it%20to%20have%20full%20autonomy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20Teslas%20with%20the%20previous-gen%20HW3%20computer%20won't%20be%20fully%20autonomous.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20owners%20may%20want%20to%20double-check%20the%20hardware%20inside%20their%20cars%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20might%20not%20have%20fully%20autonomous%20driving%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-q1-earnings-updates-tsla-stock-robotaxis-elon-musk-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst-quarter%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Teslas%20with%20Hardware%203%2C%20or%20HW3%20for%20shorthand%2C%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20unsupervised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-full-self-driving-review-limitations-fully-autonomous-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20over-the-air%20software%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20Teslas%2C%20roughly%20between%20the%20model%20years%20of%202019%20and%202023%2C%20will%20have%20an%20internal%20computer%20that's%20too%20outdated%20to%20get%20access%20to%20one%20of%20the%20key%20features%20Musk%20is%20betting%20the%20company's%20future%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20it%20were%20otherwise%2C%20but%20Hardware%203%20simply%20does%20not%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20achieve%20unsupervised%20FSD%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20the%20call.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20think%20at%20one%20point%20it%20would%20have%20that%2C%20but%20relative%20to%20Hardware%204%2C%20it%20has%20only%201%2F8%20of%20the%20memory%20bandwidth%20of%20Hardware%204.%20Memory%20bandwidth%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20elements%20needed%20for%20unsupervised%20FSD.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20and%20Musk%20have%20made%20repeated%20promises%20to%20consumers%20over%20the%20years%2C%20even%20before%20the%20release%20of%20Hardware%203%2C%20that%20their%20cars%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-subscription-only-elon-musk-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efully%20autonomous%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202016%20blog%20post%20from%20Tesla%2C%20retrieved%20via%20the%20Wayback%20Machine%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20Tesla%20vehicles%20produced%20in%20our%20factory%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Model%203%20%E2%80%94%20will%20have%20the%20hardware%20needed%20for%20full%20self-driving%20capability%20at%20a%20safety%20level%20substantially%20greater%20than%20that%20of%20a%20human%20driver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20ends%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20always%2C%20our%20over-the-air%20software%20updates%20will%20keep%20customers%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20technology%20and%20continue%20to%20make%20every%20Tesla%2C%20including%20those%20equipped%20with%20first-generation%20Autopilot%20and%20earlier%20cars%2C%20more%20capable%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-announces-new-autopilot-self-driving-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20press%20call%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20foundation%20has%20been%20laid%20for%20fully%20autonomous%2C%20it's%20twice%20as%20safe%20as%20a%20human%2C%20maybe%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20said%20older%20customers%20must%20upgrade%20their%20vehicles%20to%20achieve%20fully%20autonomous%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20in%20the%20Wednesday%20call%20that%20all%20customers%20using%20Hardware%203%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiscounted%20trade-in%26quot%3B%20to%20upgrade%20the%20car's%20computer.%20They%20will%20also%20have%20to%20replace%20the%20cameras%20on%20the%20cars%20to%20go%20with%20Hardware%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20large-scale%20upgrade%20operation%2C%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20will%20have%20to%20set%20up%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20factories%20in%20major%20metropolitan%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20doing%20it%20at%20service%20centers%20would%20be%20too%20inefficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20basically%20need%20like%20many%20production%20lines%20to%20make%20the%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20reported%20a%20total%20first-quarter%20revenue%20of%20%2422.38%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20a%2016%25%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20year%20before%2C%20beating%20analysts'%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-tesla-hardware3-fully-autonomous-self-driving-trade-in-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776916985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e98731a98bc8fdc096dc8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-tesla-hardware3-fully-autonomous-self-driving-trade-in-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20now%20a%20cut-off%20age%20for%20Teslas%20to%20have%20full%20autonomy%2C%20and%20Tesla%20wants%20you%20to%20trade%20in%20your%20older%20cars%20to%20upgrade%20their%20computer%20and%20cameras.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee%2CAditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-tesla-hardware3-fully-autonomous-self-driving-trade-in-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20built%20the%20same%20website%20using%20Lovable%20and%20Wix%20AI.%20One%20took%20twice%20as%20long%20and%20told%20me%20to%20solve%20problems%20myself.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20vibe-coded%20website%20on%20my%20monitor%20and%20my%20cat.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d8ad2a05c9b303c4e76db6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20vibe-coded%20a%20writing%20portfolio%20on%20Lovable%20and%20Wix.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20compared%20Wix%20Harmony%20and%20Lovable%20by%20building%20the%20same%20website%20using%20both%20their%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20test%20was%20to%20determine%20whether%20Wix%20had%20an%20edge%20due%20to%20its%2020%20years%20of%20website-building%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELovable%20gave%20me%20a%20cleaner%20end%20product%2C%20but%20Wix%20had%20its%20pros.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20website%20has%20never%20been%20easier%20thanks%20to%20AI.%20But%20how%20much%20easier%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe-coding%20tools%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flovable-hiring-strategy-founder-dna-structure-vibe-coding-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elike%20Lovable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-code-leak-what-happened-recreated-python-features-revealed-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthopic's%20Claude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20take%20a%20rough%20prompt%20and%20build%20a%20website%20with%20little%20to%20no%20human%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstablished%20players%20like%20Wix%20let%20individuals%20create%20websites%20without%20coding%20knowledge%2C%20but%20require%20a%20human%20user%20to%20decide%20on%20design%20elements%20and%20layout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWix%20has%20embraced%20AI%20and%20vibe%20coding%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20emerging%20rivals%20like%20Lovable.%20In%20June%20last%20year%2C%20it%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-vibecoding-tools-easy-to-copy-maor-shlomo-risk-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eacquired%20Base44%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20vibe-coding%20startup%2C%20for%20%2480%20million.%20In%20January%2C%20it%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20Wix%20Harmony%2C%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20website%20builder%20that%20merges%20human%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20as%20the%20industry%20is%20warning%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-microsoft-stocks-down-ai-replacement-future-of-software-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSaaSpocalypse%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20AI%20threatens%20the%20business%20models%20of%20companies%20like%20Workday%2C%20Salesforce%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-asana-productivity-tool-software-stocks-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20Asana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Wix's%20share%20price%20is%20down%20about%2023%25%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20partly%20on%20these%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWix's%20head%20of%20product%2C%20Yaara%20Asaf%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Wix%20Harmony%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Banyone%20who%20wants%20to%20create%20a%20web%20presence%3B%20no%20website-building%20experience%2C%20technical%20or%20design%20background%20required.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovable's%20design%20head%2C%20Nad%20Chishtie%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Lovable%20%26quot%3Bempowers%20the%2099%25%20of%20people%20with%20no%20technical%20skills%20to%20build%20whatever%20idea%20they%20have%20in%20their%20head%2C%20just%20by%20talking%20to%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20Wix%20Harmony%20to%20see%20whether%20Wix's%20two%20decades%20of%20website-building%20expertise%20gave%20it%20an%20edge%20over%20Lovable%2C%20a%202023-founded%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd7230e0-64e9-4634-b135-3c71ee2e6992%5C%22%3ELovable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lovable's%20interface.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dca61505c9b303c4e7769e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELovable%20generated%20a%20near-perfect%20website%20from%20the%20first%20prompt.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20Lovable%20before%20to%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-app-cursor-lovable-base44-vibe-coding-tools-comparison-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evirtual%20newsroom%20photo%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20already%20knew%20this%20would%20be%20a%20simple%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20threw%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-takeaways-weekend-class-build-apps-non-technical-people-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20first%20prompt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asking%20the%20platform%20to%20generate%20a%20clean%2C%20no-frills%20website%20with%20my%20headshot%20and%20bio%20on%20the%20homepage%2C%20and%20five%20sections%20%E2%80%94%20breaking%20news%2C%20careers%2C%20tech%20and%20AI%2C%20cultural%20trends%2C%20and%20retail%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20could%20post%20my%20choice%20of%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20nailed%20the%20brief%2C%20giving%20me%20almost%20exactly%20what%20I%20needed.%20The%20homepage%20features%20only%20a%20simple%20headshot%2C%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BJane%20Doe%3A%20Journalist%2C%20Reporter%2C%20Writer%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20placeholder%20bio.%20The%20website%20was%20split%20into%20five%20sections%2C%20each%20with%20three%20article%20cards%20populated%20with%20dummy%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20where%20I%20ran%20into%20my%20first%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20how%20do%20I%20edit%20the%20text%3F%20I%20expected%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanva-ceo-work-life-balance-no-email-slack-on-phone-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECanva-like%20interface%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20I%20could%20double-click%20the%20text%20box%20to%20enter%20my%20content%2C%20but%20Lovable%20didn't%20work%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20the%20chatbot%20what%20to%20do%2C%20it%20told%20me%20to%20either%20edit%20the%20code%20or%20paste%20all%20the%20edits%20into%20the%20chat%2C%20and%20it%20would%20make%20the%20changes%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20coding%20expertise%2C%20so%20I%20fed%20it%20a%20massive%20700-word%20prompt%2C%20instructing%20it%20on%20all%20the%20headlines%2C%20subheads%2C%20and%20article%20links%20to%20the%2015%20stories%20I%20wished%20to%20spotlight%20in%20my%20portfolio.%20It%20processed%20the%20request%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20realized%20the%20article%20cards%20were%20missing%20thumbnails.%20I%20asked%20if%20it%20could%20pull%20the%20thumbnails%20from%20my%20Business%20Insider%20articles%20in%20the%20correct%20dimensions.%20No%20problemo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lovable's%20interface.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dca70e96ef6a4c9d1221dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELovable%20could%20seamlessly%20populate%20the%20article%20cards%20with%20my%20input.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20all%20that%20was%20left%20was%20plonking%20my%20LinkedIn%20bio%20into%20the%20homepage%2C%20asking%20it%20to%20pull%20my%20headshot%20from%20my%20author%20page%2C%20and%20updating%20my%20contact%20info.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20I%20processed%20the%20final%20tweak%2C%20my%20daily%20free%20credits%20ran%20out.%20I%20cut%20it%20a%20bit%20close%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20it%20took%20to%20make%20the%20website%2C%20I%20had%20a%20very%20usable%20digital%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20I%20was%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285caea60-711a-4fe6-a0a5-a6ccd30e8ab9%5C%22%3EWix%20Harmony%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wix%20Harmony's%20interface.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dca76296ef6a4c9d1221dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22993%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20not%20too%20impressed%20with%20Wix's%20vibe-coded%20website%20design.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20high%20hopes%20for%20Wix%20Harmony.%20The%20first%20website%20I%20ever%20built%2C%20way%20back%20when%20I%20was%20in%20my%20high%20school's%20photography%20club%2C%20was%20a%20digital%20photo%20repository%20on%20Wix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20put%20the%20same%20prompt%20into%20Wix%20Harmony%20and%20saw%20the%20website%20it%20created%20on%20the%20first%20try%2C%20I%20sighed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20looked%20like%20all%20the%20elements%20were%20pulled%20from%20a%20basic%20PowerPoint%20template%2C%20with%20no%20consideration%20given%20to%20text%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20auto-generated%20an%20image%20of%20a%20quill%20as%20the%20website's%20logo%2C%20which%20I%20can't%20fault%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20slightly%20on%20the%20nose.%20The%20headshot%20was%20an%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20South%20Asian%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20worst%20part%20was%20that%20Wix%20didn't%20create%20five%20distinct%20sections%20for%20my%20story%20types.%20Instead%2C%20it%20lumped%20all%20the%20story%20cards%20into%20the%20homepage%20and%20hallucinated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-chatbots-hallucinate-openai-chatgpt-anthropic-claude-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20unnecessary%20sections%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20%26quot%3BBlog%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPortfolio%20page.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20prompted%20it%20to%20correct%20that%20mistake%2C%20it%20gave%20me%20a%20list%20of%20five%20steps%20to%20fix%20the%20problem%20myself%3A%20%26quot%3BFollow%20these%20steps%20to%20restructure%20your%20website%20and%20align%20the%20content%20properly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20you%20do%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20Wix.%20It%20then%20gave%20me%20another%20set%20of%20options%2C%20including%20one%20to%20contact%20Wix%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%2C%20I%20asked%20Wix%20to%20regenerate%20the%20site%2C%20thinking%20it%20might%20be%20easier%20to%20start%20afresh%20than%20fix%20all%20the%20issues%20myself.%20This%20helped%20%E2%80%94%20the%20redesign%20was%20way%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20sections%20were%20correctly%20segregated%2C%20and%20the%20text%20was%20aligned.%20But%20unlike%20Lovable%2C%20it%20couldn't%20correctly%20populate%20the%20story%20cards%20with%20information%20from%20the%2015%20stories%20I%20fed%20it%3B%20instead%2C%20it%20populated%20them%20with%20placeholder%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I've%20never%20written%20a%20story%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rise%20of%20the%20Fractional%20Leader.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wix%20interface.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dca86396ef6a4c9d1221e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWix's%20design%20was%20a%20little%20all%20over%20the%20place.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20liked%20about%20Wix%20was%20that%20it%20could%20do%20what%20Lovable%20could%20not%3A%20let%20me%20edit%20the%20text%20on%20the%20preview%20instead%20of%20putting%20my%20edits%20into%20the%20chat.%20That%20feature%20felt%20a%20lot%20more%20intuitive%20than%20Lovable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20if%20I'd%20worked%20with%20Wix's%20existing%20design%20templates%20instead%20of%20asking%20it%20to%20generate%20a%20website%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20would've%20yielded%20better%20results.%20It%20certainly%20required%20much%20more%20of%20the%20human%20touch%20than%20Lovable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b7c6cd7-f14d-422d-b7d7-d1f39340c4fd%5C%22%3EFinal%20thoughts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20impulsive%20people%20like%20myself%20who%20thrive%20on%20random%20brainwaves%20but%20don't%20have%20the%20patience%20to%20refine%20websites%2C%20Lovable%20might%20be%20a%20better%20option%2C%20as%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20draft%20up%20a%20quick%20idea%20and%20see%20it%20come%20to%20life%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChishtie%20from%20Lovable%20said%20that%20traditional%20website%20builders%20%26quot%3Bconstrain%20people's%20visions%2C%20even%20when%20they%20appear%20to%20offer%20a%20lot%20of%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tend%20to%20drive%20users%20towards%20templates%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20use%20pre-made%20blocks%20to%20create%20a%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20also%20means%20that%20customization%20comes%20with%20a%20high%20learning%20slope%2C%20as%20making%20more%20precise%20changes%20actually%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20knowledge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20got%20the%20sense%20that%20Wix%20is%20for%20someone%20more%20dedicated%20to%20the%20craft%2C%20who%20cares%20about%20how%20each%20element%20looks%20and%20wants%20more%20control%20over%20the%20flow%20of%20the%20website.%20It%20wasn't%20purely%20vibe%20coding%3A%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-on-vibe-coding-ai-tools-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-assisted%20website%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20user%20very%20much%20holding%20the%20steering%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsaf%20from%20Wix%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Wix%20Harmony%20allows%20users%20to%20seamlessly%20switch%20between%20AI%20and%20manual%20editing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20vibe%20coding%20not%20just%20a%20way%20to%20build%20websites%20quickly%2C%20but%20a%20complete%2C%20professional-grade%20method%20for%20creating%20real%2C%20live%20business%20websites%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20all%20actions%20by%20the%20AI%20tools%20were%20fully%20reversible%20and%20could%20be%20easily%20tweaked%2C%20giving%20users%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20control%20over%20the%20outcome%20at%20every%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20experience%20gave%20me%20some%20insight%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-apocalypse-salesforce-microsoft-executives-not-worried-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efears%20behind%20the%20SaaSpocalypse%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Wix's%20AI%20capabilities%20fail%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20others%20like%20Lovable%20or%20Claude%2C%20it%20risks%20losing%20users%20like%20me%20who%20are%20not%20too%20fussed%20about%20design%20and%20want%20a%20usable%20website%20in%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776916862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d8ad2a05c9b303c4e76db6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lovable%2C%20as%20a%20pure%20vibe-coding%20site%2C%20quickly%20delivered%20a%20clean%2C%20simple%20product.%20Wix%20Harmony%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20took%20more%20effort%20and%20brainpower.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%2040%20and%20%24300%2C000%20in%20debt%20after%20my%20startup%20failed.%20I'm%20living%20on%20%2410%20a%20day%20in%20South%20Korea.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20image%20of%20a%20backview%20of%20a%20man%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ce2de46a864f6fcd7bc9f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKang%20Gwang-sik%2C%2040%2C%20tells%20Business%20Insider%20he%20has%20been%20living%20on%20just%20%2410%20a%20day%20while%20facing%20%24300%2C000%20in%20debt.%3Cp%3EPlan%20Shooting%202%20%2F%20Imazins%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20South%20Korean%20man%20documented%20his%20daily%20life%20on%20just%20%2410%20a%20day%20while%20facing%20%24300%2C000%20in%20debt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKang%20Gwang-sik%2C%2040%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20went%20bankrupt%20after%20his%20business%20collapsed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20content%20creator%20shares%20how%20he's%20managing%20to%20survive%20amid%20South%20Korea's%20