%20disappointed%20in%20myself.%20I%20felt%20gloomy%20and%20isolated.%20In%20Korea%2C%20failure%20carries%20a%20lot%20of%20shame.%20If%20you%20fail%20in%20business%2C%20some%20people%20see%20you%20as%20a%20loser%20in%20a%20very%20competitive%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0d77934-a394-4ed8-91d3-327c421146a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20on%20about%20%2410%20a%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20live%20on%20about%20%2410%20a%20day.%20When%20I%20returned%20to%20work%20as%20a%20physical%20laborer%20in%20May%202025%2C%20most%20of%20that%20money%20went%20toward%20transportation%20and%20one%20simple%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20skipped%20lunch%20completely.%20Whatever%20was%20left%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20%242%20or%20%243%20%E2%80%94%20I%20carefully%20managed%20to%20get%20through%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20prices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-visiting-south-korea-first-time-american-family-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Korea%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20gone%20up%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20cook%20cheaply.%20I%20make%20simple%20Korean%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20soups%20made%20with%20cheaper%20cuts%20of%20meat%2C%20vegetables%20with%20chili%20paste%2C%20and%20basic%20home%20food.%20I%20share%20those%20meals%20online.%20People%20like%20seeing%20that%20survival%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20miserable.%20It%20can%20still%20be%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20injured%20in%20an%20accident%20at%20work%20in%20December%20%E2%80%94%20then%20I%20lost%20my%20job%2C%20and%20had%20to%20recover%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c0a85a5-b145-44b2-b978-f09638f92ed3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20made%20content%20to%20share%20my%20journey%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20the%20support%20has%20been%20heartening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20changed%20everything%20for%20me.%20Before%20the%20company%20officially%20collapsed%2C%20I%20sat%20her%20d