Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehumanoid%20robot%2C%20which%20Musk%20said%20will%20be%20%26quot%3BTesla's%20biggest%20product%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20retooling%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-model-s-x-orders-discontinued-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EModel%20S%20and%20Model%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20factory%20line%20in%20Fremont%20to%20start%20production%20for%20Optimus%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20a%20massive%20undertaking%2C%20and%20said%20he%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20watchful%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20also%20a%20little%20hesitant%20to%20show%20V3%20off%20because%20we%20find%20our%20competitors%20do%20a%20frame-by-frame%20analysis%20whenever%20we%20release%20something%20and%20copy%20everything%20they%20possibly%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20there's%20some%20value%20to%20not%20showing%20new%20technology%20until%20it's%20close%20to%20production.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20Tesla%20expects%20to%20start%20Optimus%20production%20in%20Fremont%20around%20late%20July%20or%20August.%20The%20CEO%20didn't%20name%20the%20copycat%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20said%20in%20a%20shareholder%20deck%20that%20progress%20for%20Optimus%20production%20is%20shaping%20up%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20build%20two%20factory%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20and%20another%20at%20Tesla's%20Gigafactory%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-insiders-describe-fremont-california-factory-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFremont%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20produce%20one%20million%20robots%20a%20year%2C%20while%20the%20Texas%20line%20will%20have%20a%20long-term%20annual%20production%20output%20of%2010%20million%20robots%2C%20according%20to%20the%20shareholder%20deck.%20Musk%20said%20the%20Texas%20factory%20will%20likely%20begin%20producing%20Optimus%20around%20the%20summer%20of%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20January%2C%20Tesla%20announced%20it%20would%20discontinue%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-discontinues-model-s-and-x-autonomy-robotaxi-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EModel%20S%20and%20Model%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20room%20for%20Optimus%20production%20at%20the%20Fremont%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20testing%20is%20ramping%20up%20and%20that%20Optimus%20could%20complete%20tasks%20outside%20Tesla's%20factories%20%26quot%3Bsometime%20next%20year.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHowever%2C%20the%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%20known%20for%20his%20reach-for-the-sky%20timelines%20and%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Binject%20some%20reality%26quot%3B%20into%20some%20of%20the%20questions%20raised%20on%20Wednesday%20about%20Optimus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20dismantling%20the%20production%20lines%20for%20Model%20S%20and%20Model%20X%20in%20Fremont%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20a%20few%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20installing%20a%20new%20line%20will%20take%20an%20additional%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrankly%2C%20if%20we're%20able%20to%20go%20from%20stopping%20production%20on%20one%20line%2C%20dismantling%20that%20entire%20line%2C%20reinstalling%20a%20whole%20new%20line%2C%20and%20turning%20that%20on%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20four%20months%2C%20that%20is%20an%20insanely%20fast%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20doesn't%20know%20what%20the%20production%20rate%20of%20Optimus%20will%20be%20for%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20provided%20a%20little%20more%20color%20around%20Optimus'%20current%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20Optimus%20will%20start%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-optimus-robot-new-training-austin-gigafactory-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimple%20factory%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20he%20believes%20Tesla%20will%20be%20able%20to%20pack%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20intelligence%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20robot%20locally%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Optimus%20should%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20some%20tasks%20without%20an%20internet%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimus%20will%20still%20need%20someone%20to%20tell%20it%20what%20to%20do%2C%20Musk%20said%2C%20using%20the%20analogy%20of%20a%20manager.%20He%20said%20the%20robot%20will%20need%20an%20%26quot%3Borchestration%20AI%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20guide%20it%2C%20which%20is%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-elon-musk-xai-explained-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrok%2C%20the%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20by%20xAI%2C%20will%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20interaction%20Grok%20will%20have%20with%20Optimus%20could%20be%20minimal%2C%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrok%20would%20probably%20have%20about%20as%20much%20interaction%20with%20Optimus%20as%20a%20manager%20would%20have%20with%20the%20people%20on%20their%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMeaning%20Optimus%20could%20probably%20work%20for%20several%20hours%20without%20any%20management%20oversight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-optimus-humanoid-robot-unveiling-date-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776908094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9631c3fecbb42897a3035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-optimus-humanoid-robot-unveiling-date-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20he%20expects%20production%20for%20Optimus%2C%20the%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20to%20start%20around%20late%20July%20or%20August.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ll