%3EDesperate%20buyers%20are%20in%20a%20race%20to%20secure%20a%20dwindling%20supply%20of%20secondary%20shares%20in%20Anthropic%2C%20driving%20the%20AI%20company's%20valuation%20on%20some%20sites%20to%20%241%20trillion%2C%20a%20price%20that%20would%20have%20seemed%20unthinkable%20even%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20traders%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20are%20seeing%20slumping%20demand%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20is%20now%20trading%20at%20a%20discount%20to%20Anthropic%2C%20despite%20OpenAI%20being%20valued%20at%20%24852%20billion%2C%20more%20than%20twice%20Anthropic's%20valuation%20in%20their%20most%20recent%20funding%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20valuation%20now%20hovers%20at%20around%20%241%20trillion%20on%20Forge%20Global%2C%20a%20leading%20private%20marketplace%20exchange%2C%20its%20CEO%20Kelly%20Rodriques%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20OpenAI's%20valuation%20on%20the%20platform%20is%20%24880%20billion%2C%20a%20slight%20uptick%20from%20its%20March%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20not%20yet%20public%20companies%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20investors%20are%20forced%20to%20buy%20via%20secondary%20markets%2C%20with%20existing%20stock%20in%20the%20companies%20sold%20by%20current%20or%20former%20employees%20or%20early%20investors.%20Neither%20company%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Anthropic%20shareholder%20recently%20offered%20to%20unload%20shares%20at%20a%20%241.15%20trillion%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20Ken%20Sawyer%2C%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Saints%20Capital%2C%20a%20venture%20secondary%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bvery%20well%20known%20growth%20fund%26quot%3B%20offered%20to%20buy%20Anthropic%20shares%20at%20a%20%241.05%20trillion%20valuation%2C%20Jesse%20Leimgruber%2C%20founder%20of%20OpenHome%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJesseRank%2Fstatus%2F2046730690386182629%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%