m%20VCs%20valuing%20it%20at%20as%20much%20as%20%24800%20billion%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-with-offers-to-invest-at-up-to-800-billion-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20last%20week.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20just%20received%20an%20offer%20to%20buy%20shares%20in%20Anthropic%20at%20a%20%24960%20billion%20valuation%2C%20a%20price%20he%20says%20would%20have%20been%20unthinkable%20even%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20But%20before%20he%20can%20even%20evaluate%20the%20deal%2C%20he%20expects%20it%20to%20be%20snapped%20up%20by%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20an%20offer%2C%20and%20then%20within%20a%20day%20someone%20else%20has%20already%20bought%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20almost%20no%20sellers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20own%20Anthropic%20shares%20say%20they%20are%20getting%20hounded%20with%20multiple%20offers%20a%20day%20to%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20receive%20daily%20offers%20from%20the%20ridiculous%20to%20the%20sublime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bradley%20Horowitz%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Wisdom%20Ventures%2C%20which%20was%20an%20early%20investor%20in%20both%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI.%20%26quot%3BI%20barely%20open%20those%20emails%20because%20we're%20not%20interested.%20We%20are%20playing%20a%20long%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20demand%20is%20driven%20by%20FOMO%20more%20than%20market%20fundamentals%2C%20with%20investors%20at%20venture%20firms%20and%20family%20offices%20feeling%20like%20they%20need%20to%20own%20Anthropic%20shares%20no%20matter%20the%20price%2C%20according%20to%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20less%20about%20the%20return%20than%20being%20about%20to%20say%20they're%20an%20Anthropic%20investor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20drives%20up%20the%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Anderson%20has%20seen%20little%20demand%20for%20OpenAI%20shares%20this%20year%2C%20with%20bids%20lower%20than%20its%20last%20round%20of%20%24852%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20has%20been%20a%20very%20tepid%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sentiment%20has%20certainly%20shifted%20to%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-trillion-dollar-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776904182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e94c66367066d7c296febf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-trillion-dollar-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buyers%20are%20in%20a%20race%20to%20secure%20a%20dwindling%20supply%20of%20shares%20in%20Anthropic%2C%20driving%20the%20AI%20company's%20valuation%20on%20some%20platforms%20to%20%241%20trillion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-trillion-dollar-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jon%20Favreau%20OPPOSED%20Tony%20Stark%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%20'Avengers%3A%20Endgame'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776904143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130454205%2Cimgsize-113110.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fjon-favreau-admits-he-opposed-tony-starks-death-in-avengers-endgame-had-concerns-about-fan-reactions%2Farticleshow%2F130454017.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130454017.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D