0Wasserman%2FBig%20Event%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpaceX%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20it's%20partnering%20with%20Cursor%2C%20an%20AI%20coding%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20gives%20Cursor%20access%20to%20SpaceX's%20computing%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20smart%20people%20in%20business%20and%20tech%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20multibillion-dollar%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20multibillion-dollar%20deal%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-startup-cursor-elon-musk-60-billion-spacex-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20coding%20startup%20Cursor%3C%2Fa%3E%20marks%20a%20colossal%20step%20for%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20ambitions%20to%20win%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20company%2C%20which%20owns%20AI%20startup%20xAi%2C%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20it's%20working%20with%20Cursor%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20the%20world's%20best%20coding%20and%20knowledge%20work%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20of%20Cursor's%20leading%20product%20and%20distribution%20to%20expert%20software%20engineers%20with%20SpaceX's%20million%20H100%20equivalent%20Colossus%20training%20supercomputer%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20build%20the%20world's%20most%20useful%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20cofounder%20Michael%20Truell%20said%20on%20X%20that%20he%20was%20excited%20to%20work%20with%20SpaceX%20to%20scale%20Composer%2C%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcursor-composer-chinese-model-kimi-moonshot-ai-coding-low-cost-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20coding%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20SpaceX%20gains%20the%20right%20to%20acquire%20Cursor%20later%20this%20year%20for%20%2460%20billion%2C%20or%20pay%20Cursor%20%2410%20million%20for%20the%20work%20they%20produce%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartnering%20with%20Cursor%20could%20be%20a%20crucial%20step%20for%20Musk%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20rivals%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-dario-amodei-anthropic-openai-rivalry-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20AI%20models%20hold%20a%20significant%20market%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20founded%20SpaceX%20in%202002%2C%20has%20made%20serious%20strides%20in%20AI%20this%20year.%20Chief%20among%20them%20is%20SpaceX's%20February%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-acquiring-xai-deal-elon-musk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eacquisition%20of%20Musk's%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helped%20SpaceX%20expand%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20software.%20In%20April%2C%20SpaceX%20confidentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-ipo-space-stocks-lunr-fly-yss-pl-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20for%20an%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20boosting%20gains%20in%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspace-stock-spacex-ipo-valuation-elon-musk-rklb-asts-star-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20teasing%20a%20public%20debut%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20Cursor%20deal%20electrified%20chatter%20among%20business%20and%20tech%20industry%20professionals%20on%20social%20media%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20symbiotic%20match.%20Here's%20what%20people%20in%20tech%20are%20saying%20about%20how%20the%20deal%20could%20shake%20up%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlex%20Finn%2C%20founder%20of%20Creator%20Buddy%20and%20Henry%20Intelligent%20Machines%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoltbook-ai-agents-social-network-reddit-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlex%20Finn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founder%20of%20Creator%20Buddy%20and%20AI%20agent%20startup%20Henry%20Intelligent%20Machines%2C%20said%20the%20deal%20made%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20sense%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20X%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BxAI%20has%20been%20behind%20on%20coding%20products%20for%20years%20now.%20Cursor%20has%20a%20great%20coding%20product%2C%20but%20will%20fail%20unless%20they%20build%20their%20own%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20could%20allow%20the%20two%20companies%20to%20address%20those%20issues%2C%20Finn%20said.%20While%20SpaceX%20gains%20Cursor's%20coding%20capabilities%2C%20Cursor%20gets%20access%20to%20SpaceX's%20compute%20infrastructure%20to%20build%20its%20own%20model%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20or%20Anthropic's%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinn%20said%20the%20hurdle%20Cursor%20faced%20is%20likely%20happening%20to%20many%20vibe-coding%20tools%20that%20rely%20on%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20which%20are%20building%20competing%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWins%20for%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Finn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHadley%20Harris%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Eniac%20Ventures%3Cp%3EHadley%20Harris%2C%20cofounder%20of%20seed-stage%20VC%20firm%20Eniac%20Ventures%2C%20said%20on%20X%20that%20he%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bget%26quot%3B%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20frontier%20dev%20I%20know%20has%20moved%20off%20Cursor%20and%20off%20IDEs%20entirely%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20referring%20to%20%26quot%3Bintegrated%20development%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20applications%20that%20combine%20building%2C%20editing%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20other%20coding%20capabilities.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20laggards%20are%20still%20on%20it.%20And%20dev%20tools%20always%20move%20from%20thought%20leaders%20to%20laggards%2C%20never%20the%20reverse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMario%20Nawfal%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20IBC%20Group%3Cp%3EMario%20Nawfal%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20startup%20incubator%20and%20accelerator%20IBC%20Group%2C%20said%20Cursor's%20users%20are%20largely%20%26quot%3Belite%20software%20engineers%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20an%20important%20group%20for%20SpaceX%20to%20cultivate%20ahead%20of%20an%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBringing%20in%20more%20software%20engineers%20would%20help%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20by%20extension%2C%20xAI%2C%20delve%20further%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40elonmusk%20now%20has%20space%2C%20satellites%2C%20AI%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20coding%20tool%20under%20one%20roof%2C%26quot%3B%20Nawful%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20he's%20cooking%20up%20will%20be%20wild.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETomasz%20Tunguz%2C%20founder%20and%20general%20partner%20at%20Theory%20Ventures%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftomasz-tunguz-vc-built-ai-powered-podcast-scanning-app-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETomasz%20Tunguz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20early-stage%20VC%20firm%20Theory%20Ventures%2C%20said%20the%20partnership%20allows%20SpaceX%20and%20Cursor%20to%20fill%20their%20individual%20infrastructure%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWinning%20in%20agentic%20coding%20requires%20three%20layers%3A%20compute%2C%20models%2C%20%26amp%3B%20distribution%2C%26quot%3B%20Tunguz%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BAnthropic%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Google%20own%20the%20full%20stack.%20xAI%20%26amp%3B%20Cursor%20each%20have%20gaps%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20xAI%20has%20massive%20compute%20power%2C%20referencing%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-data-center-colossus-power-memphis-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EColossus%20data%20center%20in%20Memphis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20company%20is%20losing%20popularity.%20Cursor%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20the%20opposite%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMillions%20of%20developers%20vibe%20coding%2C%20but%20its%20model%20layer%20depends%20on%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Anthropic%20%E2%80%94%20all%20competitors.%20This%20relationship%20also%20pressures%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20Tunguz%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20%2410%20billion%2C%20SpaceX%20buys%20a%20call%20option%20on%20the%20distribution%20it%20couldn't%20retain%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Cursor%20wins%20the%20independence%20it%20hasn't%20yet%20secured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESarah%20Catanzaro%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Amplify%3Cp%3EAmplify%20general%20partner%20Sarah%20Catanzaro%20reacted%20to%20the%20deal%20by%20referencing%20Elon%20Musk's%20ambitious%20plan%20to%20put%20data%20centers%20in%20space.%20Amplify%20is%20a%20VC%20focused%20on%20early-stage%20tech%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20Elon%20realized%20to%20get%20data%20centers%20in%20space%2C%20you%20first%20need%20a%20really%20good%20coding%20agent%20%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20Cantanzaro%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnand%20Kannappan%2C%20a%20former%20data%20scientist%20at%20Meta%20and%20cofounder%20of%20PatronusAI%3Cp%3EAnand%20Kannappan%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Patronus%20AI%20startup%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20deal%20wasn't%20so%20much%20a%20merger-and-acquisition%20as%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%20bet%20on%20what%20the%20real%20bottleneck%20in%20frontier%20coding%20models%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deal%20lets%20Cursor%20train%20Composer%20on%20Colossus%20while%20xAI%20runs%20the%20same%20recipe%20on%20Grok%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Kannappan%2C%20a%20former%20data%20scientist%20at%20Meta%2C%20said%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20sides%20find%20out%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20whether%20Cursor's%20data%20is%20actually%20the%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20option%20structure%20reflects%20that%20uncertainty.%20If%20the%20training%20work%20ports%20over%2C%20SpaceX%20buys%20Cursor%20and%20owns%20the%20pipeline.%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20they%20pay%20%2410B%20for%20the%20experiment%20and%20walk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20outcome%2C%20Kannappan%20said%20Musk's%20companies%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20outcome%2C%20Grok%20ends%20up%20stronger%20than%20it%20would%20have%20been%2C%20and%20xAI%20gets%20an%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20it%20couldn't%20answer%20internally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAadit%20Sheth%2C%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Narrative%20Company%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Narrative%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20a%20communications%20firm%20aimed%20at%20company%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20said%20SpaceX's%20deal%20with%20Cursor%20puts%20the%20companies%20in%20direct%20competition%20with%20industry%20leaders%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAadit%20Sheth%20said%20the%20companies%20are%20betting%20that%20Musk's%20AI%20supercomputer%20can%20train%20a%20Cursor%20model%20that%20could%20replace%20Claude%20and%20GPT.%20Both%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20working%20to%20build%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-ai-winners-startups-vibe-coding-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintegrated%20development%20environments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20help%20streamline%20software%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCursor%20has%20the%20user.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20the%20model.%20Distribution%20without%20a%20defensible%20model%20underneath%20is%20a%20rental%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheth%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20know%20in%206-12%20months%20whether%20that%20%2460B%20bought%20a%20moat%20or%20a%20rental.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EArt%20Levy%2C%20chief%20business%20officer%20at%20Brex%3Cp%3EArt%20Levy%2C%20chief%20business%20officer%20at%20fintech%20company%20Brex%2C%20said%20he%20liked%20the%20deal%20in%20a%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20'try%20before%20you%20buy'%20for%20Elon%2C%20with%20a%20massive%20'break%20up%20fee'%20for%20Cursor%20if%20it%20doesn't%20work%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Levy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20deal's%20structure%20gives%20SpaceX%20a%20call%20option%20and%20prevents%20%26quot%3Bstartup%20destruction%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20deal%20falls%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMax%20Kolysh%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Dover%3Cp%3EMax%20Kolysh%2C%20cofounder%20of%20recruiting%20startup%20Dover%2C%20said%20Cursor's%20decision%20to%20partner%20with%20SpaceX%20is%20likely%20a%20survival%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20on%20X%20that%20Cursor's%20long-term%20viability%20had%20been%20contingent%20on%20its%20access%20to%20Anthropic's%20and%20OpenAI's%20models%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20actively%20building%20Cursor%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolysh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20existential%20platform%20risk%20to%20survive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKolysh%20also%20said%20Cursor%20needs%20its%20%26quot%3Bown%20foundation%20models%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20or%20Google's%20Gemini.%20Training%20those%20requires%20deep%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20found%20the%20guy%20with%20the%20deepest%20pockets%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERohit%20Mittal%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Helium%20Ventures%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Helium%20Ventures%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20Rohit%20Mittal%20said%20the%20deal%20could%20stir%20up%20the%20AI%20startup%20scene.%20Helium%20Ventures%20acquires%20and%20guides%20software%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20very%20interesting%20if%20Claude's%20token%20consumption%20from%20Cursor%20moves%20to%20xAI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20currently%20relies%20on%20Claude%2C%20using%20its%20tokens%20%E2%80%94%20units%20of%20data%20processed%20by%20AI%20models%20%E2%80%94%20in%20its%20offerings.%20A%20new%20partnership%20could%20instead%20bring%20xAI%20into%20focus%2C%20Mittal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20imagine%20that%20impacts%20the%20growth%20rate%20of%20Claude%20(not%20saying%20it'll%20slow%20down)%2C%20but%20it'll%20pull%20xAI%20ahead%20much%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hunger%20Games%20have%20just%20begun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-cursor-deal-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776897821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e90938367066d7c296fb69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-cursor-deal-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Partnering%20with%20Cursor%20could%20be%20a%20crucial%20step%20for%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20AI%20rivals%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-cursor-deal-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Imperfect%20Women%E2%80%99%20Star%20Elisabeth%20Moss%20on%20Mary%E2%80%99s%20Suspicions%20About%20Howard%20and%20Why%20Her%20Kids%20Matter%20Most%3A%20%E2%80%98Who%20Gives%20a%20S%E2%80%94%20About%20the%20Affair%3F%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776897000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236726547%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SPOILER%20ALERT%3A%C2%A0This%20post%20contains%20stories%20from%20Episode%207%20of