aption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20love%20about%20Tello's%20no-contract%20deals%20is%20how%20you%20can%20select%20limited%20voice%20minutes%20instead%20of%20unlimited%20to%20reduce%20the%20plan's%20cost.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20solid%2010GB%20plan%20with%20unlimited%20voice%20minutes%20is%20%2415%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20even%20pay%20as%20low%20as%20%248%20a%20month%20per%20line%20for%202GB%20of%20data%20with%20300%20minutes%2C%20or%20even%20%245%20a%20month%20for%20300%20voice%20minutes%20with%20no%20data.%20We%20see%20the%20tiers%20offered%20to%20new%20customers%20change%20quite%20often%20with%20Tello.%20Not%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20options%20with%20just%201GB%20of%20data%20and%20100%20minutes%2C%20but%20as%20things%20have%20changed%2C%20those%20allowances%20have%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETello%20is%20already%20very%20cheap%20if%20you%20don't%20need%20many%20allowances%2C%20so%20there%20aren't%20any%20discounts%20for%20taking%20out%20multiple%20lines.%20When%20ordering%2C%20each%20line%20can%20be%20ordered%20individually%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20the%20same%2C%20and%20you%20can%20pay%20for%20them%20all%20with%20a%20single%20payment%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20picture%20of%20an%20iphone%20with%20tello%20plans%20and%20data%20on%20it%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7c787367066d7c296f3c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222142%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETello%20uses%20T-Mobile's%20network%20and%20advertises%20speeds%20between%2079-357Mbps%20on%205G%20connections%20and%2013-61Mbps%20on%204G.%20All%20Tello%20data%20is%20deprioritized%2C%20but%20again%2C%20we've%20never%20faced%20any%20issues%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearn%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ftello-mobile-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETello%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1eb89e9-a337-4080-a2e0-c12e9e141026%5C%22%3EFour%20main%20compromises%20with%20MVNO%20versus%20major%20carriers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221987%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20side%20bys%20ide%20of%20a%20man%20using%20a%20t-mobile%20phone%20and%20a%20verizon%20employee%20showing%20customers%20selfies%20on%20an%20iphone%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e27e75367066d7c296e18e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22994%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ET-Mobile%3B%20Verizon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20alluded%20above%20to%20the%20reduced%20support%20options%20that%20come%20with%20MVNOs.%20Few%20MVNO%20options%2C%20if%20any%2C%20have%20physical%20retail%20locations%20for%20in-person%20support%2C%20and%20most%20support%20is%20via%20phone%20or%20online%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20buy%20a%20phone%20from%20an%20MVNO%2C%20you're%20usually%20paying%20full%20price%2C%20which%20is%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20huge%20deals%20offered%20by%20major%20carriers%2C%20where%20you%20can%20get%20some%20newly%20released%20phones%20for%20free%20or%20at%20a%20big%20discount.%20However%2C%20major%20carrier%20deals%20usually%20come%20with%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20using%20the%20phone%20for%202%20or%203%20years%20before%20getting%20a%20new%20one%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20carrier.%20These%20major%20carrier%20conditions%20limit%20when%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20new%20phone%2C%20and%20might%20not%20work%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMVNOs%2C%20like%20those%20listed%20above%2C%20typically%20don't%20offer%20multi-line%20discounts%20as%20major%20carriers%20do.%20Still%2C%20two%20MVNO%20lines%20at%20full%20price%20are%20considerably%20cheaper%20than%20two%20major%20carrier%20lines%2C%20even%20with%20their%20associated%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20get%20to%20three%20or%20four%20lines%2C%20you%20can%20consider%20major%20carriers.%20Depending%20on%20the%20carrier%2C%20three-%20or%20four-line%20plans%20may%20cost%20the%20same%20or%20less%20than%20MVNO%20plans%2C%20and%20could%20even%20come%20with%20a%20free%20phone%20and%20some%20nice%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMVNOs%20don't%20usually%20offer%20perks%2C%20like%20discounts%20on%20popular%20streaming%20services.%20Verizon%2C%20for%20example%2C%20offers%20discounts%20on%20the%20Disney%2B%20bundle%2C%20the%20Netflix%20and%20Max%20bundle%2C%20Apple%20One%2C%20Apple%20Music%20Family%2C%20and%20YouTube%20Premium.%20T-Mobile%20also%20offers%20discounts%20on%20Apple%20TV%20Plus%20and%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ee48c7b-644c-4557-9e3f-e29fe30d602c%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20cell%20phone%20plans%20for%20two%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20personally%20tested%20major%20carriers%20and%20MVNOs%20to%20evaluate%20their%20network%20experience%20and%20customer%20support.%20We%20also%20assess%20the%20value%20of%20each%20plan%20offered%20by%20major%20carriers%20and%20MVNOs%2C%20and%20compare%20their%20data%20and%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two-line%20plans%2C%20specifically%2C%20we%20gauged%20the%20value%20offered%20by%20major%20carriers%20and%20MVNOs%2C%20and%20found%20that%20MVNOs%20offer%20significantly%20better%20value%20with%20little%20compromise.%20Major%20carrier%20plans%20start%20making%20more%20sense%20from%20a%20value%20standpoint%20once%20you%20have%20three%20or%20more%20lines%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22332e9837-ae9a-425c-a900-584992a2d6cb%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20you%20need%20to%20establish%20is%20which%20carrier%20network%20offers%20the%20best%20coverage%20for%20your%20area%20and%20the%20places%20you%20visit.%20A%20plan's%20value%20won't%20matter%20if%20you%20can't%20use%20it.%20We're%20ruling%20out%20major%2