%20Elephant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20no%20one%20definition%20for%20clean%20skin%20care.%20Some%20brands%20omit%20sulfates%2C%20parabens%2C%20and%20mineral%20oil%20%E2%80%94%20others%20go%20as%20far%20as%20to%20ban%20nearly%201%2C400%20questionable%20irritants%20in%20their%20products.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20is%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20that%20all%20brands%20can%20agree%20on%20is%20that%20ingredients%20should%20be%20safe%20for%20our%20bodies%20whether%20they%20are%20sourced%20naturally%20or%20produced%20in%20a%20lab.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%2011%20clean%20skin-care%20brands%20that%20rival%20anything%20else%20we've%20tried.%20In%20fact%2C%20to%20us%2C%20they're%20just%20skin-care%20brands.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsk%20anyone%20how%20they%20define%20%26quot%3Bclean%20skin%20care%26quot%3B%20and%20you'll%20get%20answers%20ranging%20from%20%26quot%3Bproducts%20made%20without%20parabens%2C%20sulfates%2C%20or%20mineral%20oils%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bthings%20you%20DIY-ed%20in%20your%20kitchen%20at%202%20a.m.%26quot%3B%20There's%20no%20right%20or%20wrong%20answer%2C%20but%20loosely%20defined%2C%20clean%20skin-care%20products%20are%20made%20without%20questionable%20ingredients%20or%20harmful%20irritants.%20Think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20safe%20than%20sorry%26quot%3B%20approach.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20one%20clear%20path%20of%20rules%20for%20clean%20beauty%2C%20much%20like%20there%20is%20no%20one%20clear%20path%20to%20'wellness.'%20They%20are%20ambiguous%20terms%20and%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20goals%20and%20preferences%20of%20each%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pamela%20Marcos%2C%20director%20of%20product%20development%20at%20Farmacy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20there%20isn't%20an%20official%20definition%2C%20brands%2C%20retailers%2C%20and%20watchdog%20organizations%20have%20created%20their%20own%20filters%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20following%20the%20European%20Union's%20list%20of%20almost%201%2C400%20banned%20ingredients%20or%20creating%20certifications%20to%20better%20educate%20consumers%20on%20what's%20safe%20or%20not.%20The%20level%20of%20clean%20among%20these%20filters%20still%20varies%20greatly%2C%20but%20just%20recognizing%20that%20certain%20ingredients%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20in%20skin-care%20products%20is%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20filler%2C%20questionable%20components%2C%20or%20toxic%20ingredients%20to%20obtain%20hydrated%20skin%2C%20shiny%20hair%2C%20and%20a%20glowing%20complexion.%20In%20fact%2C%20these%2011%20brands%20prove%20just%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20how%20some%20clean%20skin-care%20brands%20are%20setting%20a%20foundation%20in%20the%20world%20of%20beauty%20and%20wellness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESummer%20Fridays%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Summer_Fridays%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c8abc884f07ae456663d4a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESummer%20Fridays%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_051319_clean-skincare-lines-20%26h%3D85247f8e4a9445737c70a0ce707b559451283200ca9ae4da6842ec526ec0567f%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4227a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fclean-skin-care-brands%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D2417%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A