ion-of-beauty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomization%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20so%20many%20other%20aspects%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20why%20should%20we%20settle%20for%20two-in-one%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahir%20Dossa%20may%20not%20seem%20like%20your%20typical%20beauty%20brand%20founder.%20But%2C%20the%20MIT%20alum%20(with%20four%20degrees%20from%20his%20alma%20mater)%20saw%20a%20need%20for%20customization%20in%20the%20space.%20While%20receiving%20his%20PhD%2C%20Dossa%20started%20working%20on%20a%20beauty%20cooperative.%20When%20he%20asked%20a%20group%20of%20people%20for%20feedback%20on%20the%20same%20product%2C%20he%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20wide%20range%20of%20answers%20he%20received.%20It%20was%20that%20experience%20that%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20what%20would%20become%20Function%20of%20Beauty%2C%20a%20haircare%20brand%20that%20lets%20people%20customize%20their%20routine%20with%20totally%20personalized%20shampoos%20and%20conditioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20we%20thought%20after%20trying%20Function%20of%20Beauty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elisabeth%20shows%20the%20before%20and%20after%20using%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20on%20her%20curly%20hair.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60bf91bea7202d0018b8db82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElisabeth%20shows%20the%20before%20and%20after%20using%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20on%20her%20curly%20hair.%3Cp%3EElisabeth%20Chambry%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_070819_function-of-beauty-20%26h%3D588fd0cddeda15295ee47c5e6e5910a0296cca27ff3e1c5b0460dae3574ff8d0%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42606%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Ffunction-of-beauty-rev