20former%20strategic%20partnerships%20manager%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHair%20type%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elight%20brown%2C%20curly%2C%20fine%2C%20dry%20scalp%2C%20long%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProducts%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshampoo%20in%20purple%2C%20peach%20scent%3B%20conditioner%20in%20purple%2C%20peach%20scent%3B%20leave-in%20treatment%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElisabeth's%20experience%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20a%20curly-haired%20girl%2C%20I%20was%20skeptical%20of%20the%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20haircare%20products%20but%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20results.%20It%20might%20not%20be%20noticeable%20to%20the%20untrained%20eye%2C%20but%20my%20curls%20look%20more%20defined%2C%20less%20frizzy%2C%20and%20more%20moisturized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'm%20always%20searching%20for%20the%20perfect%20leave-in%20and%20curl%20cream%20combination%20for%20styling%20my%20hair.%20For%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20I've%20exclusively%20used%20my%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20leave-in%20treatment.%20It%20does%20a%20great%20job%20conditioning%20my%20curls%20and%20fighting%20frizz%20without%20weighing%20down%20my%20hair.%20The%20shampoo%20was%20sudsy%20even%20though%20it%20was%20silicone-free.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20much%20more%20conditioner%2C%20so%20the%20bottle%20is%20about%2050%25%20less%20full%20than%20my%20shampoo.%20This%20is%20common%20for%20me%20as%20a%20curly-haired%20girl%20who%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20conditioners%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20note%20it%20as%20a%20drawback.%20I%20have%20used%20other%20conditioner%20formulas%20that%20penetrated%20my%20hair%20better%2C%20making%20it%20softer%20and%20detangled%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20this%20formula%20did%20a%20fine%20job.%20The%20bottles%20are%20a%20joy%20to%20have%20in%20the%20shower%2C%20but%20the%20pumps%20also%20lock%20easily%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20my%20scalp%2C%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20difference%20in%20ridding%20flakes%20and%20dryness.%20I've%20had%20trouble%20finding%20a%20haircare%20product%20that%20competes%20with%20my%20simple%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20rinses.%20I'll%20likely%20continue%20my%20treasure%20hunt%20to%20find%20something%20that%20absolutely%20blows%20me%20away%2C%20but%20I'll%20keep%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20in%20my%20back%20pocket%20for%20a%20reliable%20and%20fun-to-have%20haircare%20system.%20Finding%20products%20that%20work%20for%20my%20hair%20is%20pretty%20difficult%2C%20but%20I%20enjoy%20the%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Connie%20Chen%20shows%20the%20before%20and%20after%20using%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20on%20her%20color-treated%20hair.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60bf9ec6a7202d0018b8dbe1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConnie%20Chen%20shows%20the%20before%20and%20after%20using%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20on%20her%20color-treated%20hair.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnie%20Chen%2C%20former%20senior%20reporter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHair%20type%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edark%20brown%20(color-treated)%2C%20medium%20coarseness%2C%20straight%2C%20medium-length%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProducts%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshampoo%20in%20purple%2C%20pear%20scent%3B%20conditioner%20in%20blue%2C%20pear%20scent%3B%20hair%20mask%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnie's%20experience%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20most%20haircare%2C%20it%20often%20feels%20like%20I%20have%20to%20compromise%20somewhere%2C%20whether%20it's%20an%20ingredient%20I%20don't%20want%20in%20the%20formulation%20or%20being%20pigeonholed%20into%20certain%20fragrances.%20I%20love%20that%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20gives%20me%20way%20more%20control.%20I%20have%20dyed%20hair%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20choose%20a%20purple%20shampoo%20to%20reduce%20brassiness.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20could%20choose%20to%20have%20my%20products%20address%20my%20specific%20hair%20goals%2C%20which%20include%20strengthening%20and%20conditioning%20with%20a%20nice%20smelling%20formula.%20Over%20the%20last%20six%20weeks%2C%20I've%20used%20the%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner%20every%20other%20day.%20I%20apply%20the%20hair%20mask%20once%20a%20week%20and%20my%20hair%20looks%20and%20feels%20much%20healthier.%20A%20plus%20is%20that%20all%20the%20fragrances%20smell%20amazing%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20tried%20the%20pear%2C%20peach%2C%20and%20mango%20over%20the%20years%20and%20they're%20some%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20haircare%20scents%20I've%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlyssa%20Powell%2C%20graphic%20designer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alyssa's%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20custom%20haircare%20lineup%20includes%3A%20turquoise%20shampoo%20and%20purple%20conditioner.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60aea643bee0fc0019d59c3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlyssa's%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20custom%20haircare%20lineup%20includes%3A%20turquoise%20shampoo%20and%20purple%20conditioner.%3Cp%3EAlyssa%20Powell%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHair%20type%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20black%2C%20tightly%20coiled%2C%20short%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProducts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20shampoo%20in%20turquoise%2C%20lavender%20scent%3B%20conditioner%20in%20purple%2C%20lavender%20scent%3B%20both%20silicone-free%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlyssa's%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20As%20much%20as%20I%20love%20my%20tightly%20coiled%2C%20well-put-together%20hair%2C%20maintaining%20moisture%2C%20retaining%20length%2C%20and%20finding%20the%20right%20products%20have%20always%20been%20a%20struggle%20for%20me.%20So%20I%20chose%20the%20following%20hair%20goals%20when%20customizing%3A%20curl%20definition%2C%20hydrate%2C%20and%20strengthen.%20I%20also%20chose%20to%20get%20the%20silicone-free%20formula%20for%20both%2C%20in%20the%20True%20L(o)vender%20scent%20because%20it%20was%20100%25%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packaging%20of%20these%20products%20was%20beautiful.%20I%20loved%20my%20name%20printed%20on%20the%20bottles%20and%20on%20the%20direction%20booklet.%20When%20I%20tried%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20last%20year%2C%20I%20was%20not%20impressed.%20However%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20another%20try%20because%20I%20finally%20found%20a%20wash%20routine%20that%20had%20been%20working%20for%20me.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20products%20properly%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20followed%20my%20normal%20routine%3A%20shampooing%20once%20a%20week%2C%20using%20conditioner%20every%20other%20day%2C%20then%20following%20up%20with%20a%20leave-in%20gel%20from%20another%20brand.%20I%20let%20the%20conditioner%20sit%20for%20the%20directed%205-10%20minutes.%20I%20liked%20the%20way%20my%20hair%20felt%20after%20using%20the%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner.%20It%20was%20clean%2C%20moisturized%2C%20and%20the%20products%20smelled%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20month%20of%20using%20the%20products%2C%20I%20think%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20has%20earned%20a%20spot%20on%20my%20bathroom%20shelf.%20Having%20a%20consistent%20routine%20and%20following%20the%20directions%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mara's%20custom%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20lineup%20includes%3A%20a%20purple%20shampoo%2C%20white%20conditioner%2C%20hair%20serum%2C%20and%20body%20lotion.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60cb567720bd1300181c6ca5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMara's%20custom%20Function%20of%20Beauty%20lineup%20includes%3A%20a%20purple%20shampoo%2C%20white%20conditioner%2C%20hair%20serum%2C%20and%20body%20lotion.%3Cp%3EMara%20Leighton%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMara%20Leighton%2C%20senior%20reporter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3EHair%20type%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20brunette%20(color-treated)%2C%20thick%2C%20wavy%2C%20long%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3EProducts%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshampoo%20in%20purple%2C%20eucalyptus%20scent%3B%20conditioner%20in%20white%2C%20eucalyptus%20scent%3B%20body%20lotion%20in%20eucalyptus%20scent%3B%20hair%20serum%20in%20pear%20scent%3B%20body%20wash%20in%20white%2C%20eucalyptus%20scent%3B%20body%20lotion%20in%20white%2C%20eucalyptus%20scent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3EMara's%20experience%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMy%20hair%20can%20be%20as%20dry%20and%20frizzy%20as%20grass%20in%20a%20drought%2C%20so%20I%20tend%20to%20favor%20hydrating%20products%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20loved%20Function%20of%20Beauty's%20formulas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20customize%20my%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner%20to%20include%20the%20stuff%20I%20know%20I%20need%20but%20hate%20looking%20for%20in%20ingredient%20lists%2C%20such%20as%20ingredients%20to%20combat%20brassiness%20in%20color-treated%20hair%20and%20nutritious%20oils%20to%20smooth%20and%20hydrate.%20Personally%2C%20I%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20option%20to%20pick%20the%20color.%20But%20most%20importantly%20is%20that%20my%20hair%20consistently%20dried%20looking%20more%20hydrated%20and%20less%20frizzy%2C%20but%20still%20clean%20and%20voluminous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20could%20only%20buy%20one%20thing%20again%2C%20though%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20Hair%20Serum.%20It%20makes%20my%20hair%20look%20so%20uncharacteristically%20hydrated%2C%20shiny%2C%20and%20more%20defined%20(the%20qualities%20I%20find%20most%20difficult%20to%20replicate)%20without%20edging%20on%20greasy.%20It's%20also%20more%20manageable%20after%20I've%20applied%20the%20Hair%20Serum.%20I've%20definitely%20used%20too%20much%20before%2C%20but%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20that's%20difficult%20to%20do%3B%20my%20hair%20drinks%20this%20formula%20up.%20And%20the%20pear%20scent%20smells%20really%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lotion%20and%20body%20wash%20are%20nice%20but%20don't%20reinvent%20the%20wheel%20(and%20they%20don't%20need%20to).%20My%20one%20nitpick%20is%20that%20I%20wish%20I'd%20gone%20for%20light%20strength%20on%20the%20fragrances.%20I%20chose%20the%20fresh%2C%20clean%20eucalyptus%20(which%20smells%20a%20lot%20like%20mint)%20for%20most%20of%20the%20products%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20slightly%20heavy%20for%20my%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20create%20your%20personalized%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20your%20own%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_070819_function-of-beauty-20%26h%3D588fd0cddeda15295ee47c5e6e5910a0296cca27ff3e1c5b0460dae3574ff8d0%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42606%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Ffunction-of-beauty-review-custom-shampoo-and-conditioner%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.functionofbeauty.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFunction%20of%20Beauty%3C%2Fa%3E%20haircare%20is%20simple.%20You'll%20follow%20these%20steps%20to%20get%20a%20customized%20formula%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_070819_function-of-beauty-20%26h%3De91162b059766a4c8bba59323ce1adba21e27b9b369b212d382061102f60f562%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42606%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Ffunctio