izer%20(%2448)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20aforementioned%20Green%20Smoothie%20for%20your%20skin%20%E2%80%94%20packed%20with%20kale%2C%20spinach%2C%20green%20tea%2C%20and%20the%20skincare%20heavyweight%20hyaluronic%20acid%20for%20added%20moisture.%20The%20operative%20word%20here%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhip%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20product%20hydrates%2C%20but%20one%20aspect%20of%20its%20lightweight%20texture%20is%20that%20it's%20able%20to%20be%20absorbed%20quickly%20and%20without%20leaving%20a%20residue.%20YTTP%20recommends%20using%20it%20after%20a%20serum%2C%20and%20I'd%20echo%20that%20sentiment%20for%20maximum%20hydration.%20It%20worked%20well%20for%20me%20especially%20in%20conjunction%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1715772459644739094%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlow%20Oil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20extra%20dry%20skin%20might%20warrant%20more%20product%20than%20makes%20sense%20at%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1715772508794495633%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Superfood%20Antioxidant%20Cleanser%20(%2436)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20antioxidant-rich%20gel%20cleanser%20with%20many%20of%20the%20same%20ingredients%20as%20the%20Air-Whip%20(kale%2C%20spinach%2C%20green%20tea)%20to%20remove%20toxins%20without%20stripping%20the%20skin%20with%20harsher%20ingredients.%20Like%20all%20YTTP%20products%2C%20it's%20formulated%20without%20most%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bdon't%26quot%3Bs%20that%20can%20lurk%20in%20your%20cleansers%2C%20like%20sulfates%2C%20soap%2C%20fragrances%2C%20or%20parabens.%20True%20to%20its%20word%2C%20it's%20gentle%2C%20non-drying%2C%20and%20removes%20makeup%20easily.%20As%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fno-bs-skincare-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan