gure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227305%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20wearing%20camouflage%20crouches%20and%20works%20on%20a%20small%20drone%20with%20a%20blue%20cloudy%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e91a593fecbb42897a2ccf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdm.%20Paparo%20said%20US%20forces%20need%20cheap%20weapons%20for%20less%20exquisite%20targets.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Duke%20Edwards%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20needs%20a%20deeper%20magazine%20of%20cheap%20precision-kill%20weapons%20like%20drones%2C%20Adm.%20Samuel%20Paparo%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20INDOPACOM%20leader%20noted%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20range%20of%20weapons%20for%20different%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20military%20leaders%20are%20seeing%20the%20value%20of%20lower-cost%20weapons%2C%20like%20LUCAS%20drones%2C%20in%20certain%20situations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20forces%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20building%20of%20a%20larger%20arsenal%20of%20cheap%2C%20precision-kill%20weapons%20or%20risk%20losing%20a%20future%20war%2C%20America's%20top%20commander%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow-cost%20systems%20like%20cheap%20drones%20and%20inexpensive%20missile%20designs%20have%20had%20a%20fundamental%20impact%20on%20conflicts%20like%20Russia's%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20US%20war%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20military%20leaders%20argue%20that%20fielding%20large%20numbers%20of%20lower-cost%20weapons%20for%20missions%20where%20high-end%20systems%20aren%E2%80%99t%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20like%20shooting%20down%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20can%20ease%20the%20cost%20trade-offs%2C%20especially%20against%20adversaries%20with%20deep%20arsenals%20like%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20these%20systems%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20commoditization%20of%20cheap%2C%20distributed%2C%20precision%20kill%20%5Bweapons%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20something%20seen%20every%20day%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-could-prevent-us-air-superiority-first-island-chain-admiral-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdm.%20Samuel%20Paparo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20told%20the%20US%20House%20Armed%20Services%20Committee%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20technology%20that%20we%20embrace%2C%20or%20we%20lose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaparo%20said%20that%20these%20weapons%20are%20particularly%20critical%20in%20denying%20or%20defending%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20preventing%20an%20adversary%20from%20controlling%20certain%20maritime%20or%20air%20spaces.%20Anti-access%20and%20area-denial%20strategies%20rely%20on%20a%20mix%20of%20weaponry%20that's%20spread%20out%20and%20layered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20broad%20A2%2FAD%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20relies%20on%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20missile%20defenses%2C%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20naval%20capabilities%20that%20would%20challenge%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20from%20operating%20freely%20in%20and%20around%20the%20First%20Island%20Chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Paparo%20pointed%20to%20the%20US-made%20Merops%20interceptor%20drone%20system%20as%20a%20low-cost%20defensive%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20proven%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20US%20has%20purchased%20thousands%20of%20thse%20for%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20offensive%20action%2C%20the%20admiral%20noted%20that%20war%20with%20Iran%20had%20demonstrated%20the%20success%20of%20the%20new%20Low-Cost%20Unmanned%20Combat%20Attack%20System%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-military-force-used-cheap-attack-drones-first-time-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELUCAS%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20American-made%20one-way%20attack%20weapon%20based%20on%20the%20Iranian-designed%20Shahed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227361%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20holds%20a%20drone%20at%20night%20in%20the%20dark.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e91ac3367066d7c296fbe7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224910%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaparo%20previously%20said%20his%20intent%20is%20to%20turn%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bhellscape%26quot%3B%20of%20uncrewed%20systems%20and%20drones%20should%20China%20invade%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Olivia%20Cowart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20deployed%20LUCAS%20in%20combat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20following%20US%20Central%20Command's%20creation%20in%20December%20of%20a%20new%20task%20force%20built%20around%20the%20military's%20first%20LUCAS%20one-way%20attack%20drone%20squadron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20fiscal%20year%202027%20budget%2C%20the%20White%20House%20is%20requesting%20over%20%2474%20billion%20for%20drones%20and%20counter-drone%20solutions.%20That%20figure%20is%20triple%20what%20the%20US%20spent%20on%20these%20areas%20in%202026%20and%20the%20largest%20investment%20in%20these%20capabilities%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaparo%20said%20that%20the%20substantial%20request%20was%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20theater%20where%20we%20must%20have%20the%20concepts%20in%20order%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20deploying%20low-cost%20drones%20and%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaparo%20made%20waves%20in%20June%202024%20when%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20turn%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Taiwan%20Strait%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-plans-turn-taiwan-strait-into-drone-hellscape-against-china-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunmanned%20hellscape%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20employ%20a%20strategy%20inspired%20by%20Ukraine%20that%20would%20flood%20the%20battlespace%20with%20drones%20and%20other%20uncrewed%20systems%2C%20the%20aim%20being%20to%20blunt%20a%20Chinese%20assault%20and%20buy%20time%20for%20reinforcements%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20those%20comments%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Taiwan%20have%20continued%20investing%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-needs-both-sophisticated-asymmetric-weapons-for-china-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Easymmetric%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20cheap%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20and%20distributed.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20they%20launched%20a%20joint%20effort%20to%20prepare%20Taiwanese%20forces%20for%20just%20that%20kind%20of%20fight%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20uncrewed%20systems%20and%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Tuesday's%20hearing%2C%20Paparo%20added%20that%20the%20US%20was%20also%20investing%20in%20low-cost%20hypersonic%20missiles%20and%20low-cost%20cruise%20missiles%20because%20these%20systems%20added%20more%20options%20to%20the%20US%20arsenal.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20need%20exquisite%20to%20take%20down%20exquisite%20things%2C%20we%20need%20cheap%20to%20take%20out%20less%20exquisite%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepartment%20of%20Defense%20leaders%20and%20officials%20have%20increasingly%20spotlighted%20the%20need%20for%20cost-effective%20munitions%20so%20that%20troops%20aren't%20firing%20multimillion-dollar%20weapons%20to%20take%20out%20drones%20that%20cost%20a%20fraction%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELUCAS%20drones%2C%20for%20example%2C%20cost%20around%20%2435%2C000%20per%20unit%2C%20far%20less%20than%20a%20cruise%20or%20ballistic%20missile%2C%20while%20the%20Merops%20interceptor%20drones%20cost%20just%20%2415%2C000%20compared%20to%20the%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20Shaheds%20these%20weapons%20were%20designed%20to%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20conflicts%20have%20demonstrated%20the%20cost%20and%20stockpile%20concerns%20associated%20with%20expending%20expensive%2C%20exquisite%20systems%20against%20cheaper%20targets.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-learning-curve-right-weapons-red-sea-fight-admiral-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20conflict%20against%20the%20Houthis%3C%2Fa%3E%20drained%20the%20US%20Navy%20of%20critical%20munitions%2C%20while%20American%20forces%20have%20burned%20through%20weapons%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-war-with-iran-by-numbers-energy-drinks-to-targets-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETomahawk%20cruise%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-risks-future-loss-without-cheap-precision-kill-weapons-adm-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776890275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e91c303fecbb42897a2cea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-risks-future-loss-without-cheap-precision-kill-weapons-adm-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20need%20exquisite%20to%20take%20down%20exquisite%20things%2C%20we%20need%20to%20cheap%20to%20take%20out%20less%20exquisite%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Adm.%20Paparo%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-risks-future-loss-without-cheap-precision-kill-weapons-adm-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TCL%20QM8L%20SQD%204K%20TV%20review%3A%20Rich%20color%20and%20bright%20HDR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%