%20but%20my%20testing%20results%20will%20generally%20apply%20across%20the%20full%20lineup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM8L%20has%20an%20attractive%20build%20that's%20a%20step%20above%20cheaper%20TCL%20models%2C%20but%20not%20quite%20as%20premium%20as%20the%20brand's%20more%20expensive%20X11L.%20The%20panel%20is%20about%20two%20inches%20deep%20at%20its%20thickest%20point.%20That's%20relatively%20slim%20for%20a%20Mini%20LED%20TV%2C%20but%20not%20as%20thin%20as%20the%20X11L's%20impressive%200.8-inch%20profile.%20The%20frame%20around%20the%20TV%20has%20a%20silver%20accent%2C%20and%20the%20screen%20uses%20TCL's%20ZeroBorder%20design%2C%20so%20there's%20virtually%20no%20black%20bezel%20around%20the%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20included%20pedestal%20stand%20is%20sturdy%20and%20attractive%2C%20but%20it%20might%20not%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20some%20soundbar%20setups.%20Though%20the%20stand%20can%20be%20attached%20in%20a%20low%20or%20high%20position%2C%20its%20depth%20is%2014.5%20inches.%20That's%20a%20pretty%20big%20footprint%2C%20so%20it's%20possible%20your%20media%20console%20won't%20be%20deep%20enough%20to%20fit%20a%20soundbar%20in%20front%20without%20resting%20it%20on%20the%20pedestal%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal.%20This%20is%20a%20minor%20drawback%2C%20but%20one%20that%20soundbar%20owners%20should%20be%20aware%20of.%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%2098-inch%20model%20uses%20left%20and%20right%20feet%20rather%20than%20a%20pedestal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM8L%20TV%20remote%20control%20in%20a%20person's%20hand%20with%20the%20TV%20out%20of%20focus%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7e46a3fecbb42897a2633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETCL's%20remote%20has%20handy%20backlit%20keys%2C%20which%20LG%20and%20Samsung%20remotes%20are%20missing.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcapti