8L%204K%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20red%20dress%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20city%20with%20balloons%20flying%20overhead.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8e041a98bc8fdc096d688%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM8L's%20color%20capabilities%20are%20a%20step%20above%20typical%20QLED%20TVs.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM8L's%20biggest%20upgrade%20over%20last%20year's%20QM8K%20is%20the%20addition%20of%20TCL's%20new%20SQD%20(Super%20Quantum%20Dot)%20technology.%20SQD%20tech%20debuted%20on%20the%20company's%20premium%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ftcl-x11l-sqd-4k-qled-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EX11L%2C%20which%20I%20previously%20reviewed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20SQD%20might%20sound%20like%20just%20another%20flashy%20branding%20term%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20there's%20actual%20substance%20behind%20the%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETCL's%20SQD%20system%20uses%20larger%20quantum%20dots%20than%20on%20a%20typical%20QLED%20TV%2C%20along%20with%20an%20enhanced%20color%20filter%2C%20to%20produce%20a%20wider%2C%20brighter%20color%20range.%20This%20same%20technology%20helped%20make%20the%20X11L%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impressive%20TVs%20I've%20ever%20tested%2C%20so%20it's%20great%20to%20see%20TCL%20bringing%20it%20down%20to%20a%20more%20affordable%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20match%20the%20X11L's%20overall%20image%20quality.%20The%20X11L%20still%20has%20the%20edge%20in%20a%20few%20key%20areas%2C%20like%20local%20dimming%20and%20peak%20brightness.%20But%20the%20QM8L%20gets%20very%20close%20in%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20colorimeter%20with%20Calman%20software%20and%20a%20Portrait%20Displays%20G1%20pattern%20generator%2C%20I%20measured%20the%20TV's%20color%20gamut%20at%20about%2085%25%20of%20the%20BT.2020%20color%20space.%20BT.2020%20is%20currently%20the%20widest%20color%20gamut%20used%20for%20Hollywood%20productions%2C%20and%20most%20regular%20QLEDs%20can%20cover%20about%2060%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20other%20TVs%20I've%20recently%20tested%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20trails%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3Daa2b9cc16d4544c290537b0ec848afbf32a9b1fb70d743ff2d57f395f6d55fc4%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-Ultimate-Brightness-Contrast%252Fdp%252FB0GFDJGFG7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX11L%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Samsung's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-r95h-micro-rgb-tv-review%5C%22%20t