20banding%2C%20which%20is%20great%20given%20how%20often%20those%20scenes%20can%20expose%20blocky%20colors%20on%20many%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213c80cf5-db34-4a1f-988a-9c0bfc0dc7c6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Brightness%20and%20contrast%5C%22%3EBrightness%20is%20excellent%2C%20but%20OLEDs%20and%20the%20pricier%20TCL%20X11L%20still%20have%20an%20edge%20in%20contrast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221990%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20QM8L%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20building%20with%20the%20sun%20in%20the%20sky%20on%20its%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8e105a98bc8fdc096d6a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20display%20delivers%20excellent%20HDR%20brightness%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20fit%20for%20both%20home%20theaters%20and%20average%20living%20rooms.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHDR%20brightness%20is%20another%20clear%20strength.%20On%20a%2010%25%20HDR%20test%20pattern%2C%20with%20Filmmaker%20Mode%2C%20dynamic%20tone%20mapping%20off%2C%20and%20local%20dimming%20set%20to%20high%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20peak%20brightness%20of%20around%203%2C600%20nits%2C%20with%20occasional%20bursts%20up%20to%204%2C100%20nits%2C%20which%20is%20about%20on%20par%20with%20last%20year's%20model.%20However%2C%20when%20measuring%20again%20after%20the%20TV%20had%20been%20on%20for%20a%20while%2C%20that%20number%20dropped%20to%20around%202%2C000%20nits%2C%20which%20the%20set%20had%20no%20trouble%20sustaining.%20So%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20around%202%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20nits%20of%20peak%20HDR%20brightness%20depending%20on%20how%20long%20highlights%20appear%20on%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20numbers%20don't%20quite%20match%20the%20X11L%2C%20which%20could%20sustain%203%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20nits%20and%20hit%20around%206%2C000%20nits%20in%20bursts%20with%20similar%20settings%2C%20but%20the%20QM8L%20is%20still%20bright%20enough%20to%20accurately%20reproduce%20highlight%20intensity%20in%20most%20HDR%20content.%20That%20means%20specular%20highlights%20have%20excellent%20punch.%20Reflections%2C%20sparks%2C%20sunlight%2C%20and%20explosions%20all%20pop%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20impact%20that%20makes%20premium%20HDR%20content%20look%20premium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20dimming%20is%20also%20very%20good%20for%20a%20Mini%20LED%20TV%2C%20though%20not%20quite%20as%20refined%20as%20what%20you%20get%20from%20TCL's%20step-up%20X11L.%20In%20most%20material%2C%20black%20levels%20look%20deep%20and%20uniform%2C%20and%20the%20TV%20does%20a%20convincing%20job%20balancing%20bright%20highlights%20against%20dark%20backgrounds.%20But%20in%20tricky%20scenes%2C%20I%20could%20spot%20the%20backlight%20at%20work%20more%20than%20I%20could%20on%20the%20X11L.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dark%20sequence%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Green%20Knight%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20a%20character%20enters%20an%20abandoned%20house%20at%20night%2C%20revealed%20subtle%20patchiness%20and%20flickering%20in%20shadows.%20I%20could%20also%20see%20hints%20of%20blooming%20around%20a%20character's%20glowing%20eyes.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20burning%20church%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20showed%20minor%20inconsistencies%20in%20black%20levels%2C%20with%20some%20areas%20of%20the%20screen%20looking%20beautifully%20deep%20and%20others%20appearing%20slightly%20elevated%20or%20vignetted.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20few%20episodes%20of%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20on%20Disney%2B%2C%20I%20spotted%20faint%20darkened%20outlines%20around%20characters%20on%20dim%20backgrounds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20you%20often%20have%20to%20know%20what%20to%20look%20for%20to%20see%20these%20kinds%20of%20flaws%2C%20and%20they're%20most%20evident%20in%20a%20pitch-black%20room.%20Most%20people%20probably%20won't%20see%20them%20during%20regular%20viewing%2C%20and%20even%20as%20someone%20who%20specifically%20hunts%20for%20this%20sort%20of%20thing%2C%20I%20found%20them%20relatively%20minor.%20Still%2C%20they're%20there%2C%20and%20they%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20even%20a%20really%20good%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20still%20can't%20match%20the%20precision%20of%20an%20OLED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221798%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM8L%204K%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20an%20image%20of%20an%20iguana%20on%20its%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8e09e367066d7c296f963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM8L's%20off-axis%20viewing%20is%20better%20than%20that%20of%20an%20average%20QLED%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20not%20on%20par%20with%20an%20OLED.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20though%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20avoids%20one%20issue%20I%20noticed%20on%20the%20more%20expensive%20X11L%3A%20faint%20vertical%20streaking%20on%20black%20backgrounds.%20I%20didn't%20see%20that%20artifact%20here%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20win%20for%20the%20cheaper%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20at%20least%20one%20area%2C%20I%20actually%20preferred%20the%20QM8L's%20presentation%20to%20the%20X11L's.%20In%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%2C%26quot%3B%20certain%20HDR%20highlights%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20explosions%20and%20bright%20reflections%20on%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20looked%20a%20bit%20more%20dynamic%20on%20the%20QM8L.%20On%20the%20X11L%2C%20the%20centers%20of%20those%20highlights%20occasionally%20looked%20a%20touch%20faded%2C%20while%20the%20QM8L%20preserved%20a%20little%20more%20punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewing%20angles%2C%20however%2C%20remain%20just%20OK.%20As%20with%20the%20X11L%2C%20TCL's%20SQD%20tech%20doesn't%20do%20much%20to%20improve%20the%20off-axis%20weaknesses%20common%20to%20LED%2FLCD%20displays.%20The%20QM8L%20performs%20a%20bit%20better%20than%20a%20typical%20QLED%2C%20but%20colors%20and%20contrast%20still%20fade%20and%20distort%20somewhat%20toward%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20screen.%20My%20usual%20%26quot%3BEx%20Machina%26quot%3B%20test%20scene%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20this%2C%20since%20the%20red%20lighting%20in%20that%20sequence%20shifts%20toward%20orange%20as%20you%20move%20off-center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReflection-handling%20is%20decent%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20TV%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20headroom%20to%20pump%20up%20brightness%20in%20order%20to%20overcome%20glare.%20However%2C%20the%20panel%20is%20still%20glossy%2C%20so%20direct%20reflections%20in%20bright%20rooms%20will%20be%20visible.%20If%20reflections%20are%20a%20big%20issue%2C%20you're%20still%20better%20off%20with%20one%20of%20Samsung's%20glare-free%20TV%20models%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3De5539d3892e0550f64ac93846b951e00bd67521d7bbadbe68142187a0a26a58c%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Ftvs%252Fmicro-rgb%252F65-inch-micro-rgb-4k-tv-r95h-sku-mrn65r95hafxza%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ER95H%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-2026-s90h-s95h-s85h-oled-4k-tvs-price-impressions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ES95H%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20movies%20and%20shows%2C%20the%20TV's%20image%20quality%20also%20translates%20well%20to%20video%20games%2C%20which%20look%20similarly%20vibrant%20and%20bright%2C%20particularly%20when%20titles%20support%20HDR.%20I%20also%20found%20motion%20to%20be%20smooth%20when%20engaging%20the%20TV's%20120Hz%20mode%20and%20VRR%20(variable%20refresh%20rate)%20in%20PS5%20games%20like%20%26quot%3BMarvel's%20Spider-Man.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20I%20noticed%20some%20flicker%20when%20using%20120Hz%20with%20VRR%20in%20%26quot%3BCrimson%20Desert.%26quot%3B%20I%20also%20noticed%20this%20with%20the%20X11L%2C%20so%20it%20could%20be%20an%20isolated%20VRR%20issue%20with%20that%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e93ed6c9-7a55-450a-b474-23a7b73dc135%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20features%5C%22%3EGoogle%20TV%20with%20Gemini%20is%20a%20great%20all-around%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221772%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20QM8L%20SQD%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20the%20Google%20TV%20homepage%20on%20its%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8dfd8a98bc8fdc096d67c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221329%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20TV's%20layout%20is%20clean%20and%20simple%20to%20navigate%2C%20with%20recommendations%20you%20might%20actually%20want%20to%20watch.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20TCL%20Mini%20LED%20TVs%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20uses%20the%20Google%20TV%20platform%20with%20Gemini%20AI%20built%20in.%20Though%20I%20used%20to%20have%20a%20few%20qualms%20about%20Google's%20smart%20TV%20platform%20(especially%20back%20in%20the%20Android%20TV%20days)%2C%20its%20latest%20iteration%20has%20become%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20interfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20TV%20syncs%20seamlessly%20with%20an%20existing%20Google%20account%2C%20which%20makes%20setup%20a%20breeze%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20use%20a%20phone%20with%20the%20Google%20Home%20app.%20The%20on-screen%20design%20is%20easy%20to%20navigate%20with%20quick%20access%20to%20your%20downloaded%20apps%20on%20a%20horizontal%20menu%20that's%20up%20front%20and%20center.%20There%20are%20also%20rows%20of%20content%20recommendations%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20obtrusive%2C%20and%20they%20tend%20to%20include%20titles%20I'd%20actually%20want%20to%20watch.%20The%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20recommendations%20highlighted%20on%20many%20rival%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20is%20also%20a%20good%20digital%20assistant.%20It's%20responsive%2C%20understands%20conversational%20queries%20with%20follow-ups%2C%20and%20is%20great%20for%20content%20discovery.%20It's%20also%20capable%20of%20other%20advanced%20tasks%2C%20like%20helping%20to%20plan%20a%20trip%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20find%20those%20capabilities%20all%20that%20necessary%20for%20a%20TV.%20You%20can%20use%20Gemini%20with%20the%20included%20remote%20or%20hands-free%20with%20the%20TV's%20integrated%20microphone%20that%20can%20also%20be%20deactivated%20for%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigation%20speed%20is%20smooth%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20notable%20hiccups.%20Older%20TCL%20TVs%20were%20known%20for%20occasional%20glitches%20with%20settings%20and%20menus%2C%20but%20the%20brand%20has%20seemingly%20ironed%20out%20those%20kinks%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20During%20my%20testing%20time%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20delivered%20a%20painless%2C%20bug-free%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238123383-b772-4fce-842d-6ab27ca226e0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20TCL%20QM8L%20SQD%204K%20TV%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222235%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20QM8L%20SQD%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20a%20video%20of%20a%20mountain%20range%20by%20a%20lake%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7e4de3fecbb42897a2639%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM8L%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20TVs%20of%202026%2C%20but%20last%20year's%20cheaper%20QM8K%20remains%20a%20better%20value%20for%20most%20people.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151262905599o-20%26h%3D0dc2a9e19767e58c2312fcb3253e55893958477009ea17ca7dba555db3be8fee%26postID%3D69e7ce3e215b3a0a3c7e6ef7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm8l-sqd-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTCL-SQD-Mini-LED-65QM8L-Brightness-Television%252Fdp%252FB0GPSFR1Q4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETCL%20QM8L%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20follow-up%20to%20last%20year's%20already%20fantastic%20QM8K.%20It%20carries