-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fyoung-trump-official-breaks-silence-on-sugar-daddy-scandal-says-its-just-a-relationship-turned-sour%2Famp_articleshow%2F130451602.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fyoung-trump-official-breaks-silence-on-sugar-daddy-scandal-says-its-just-a-relationship-turned-sour%2Famp_articleshow%2F130451602.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ServiceNow%20CEO%20dismisses%20AI%20software%20threats%20as%20'parlor%20tricks'%20as%20he%20raises%20forecasts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ServiceNow%20CEO%20Bill%20McDermott%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e92161a98bc8fdc096d951%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EServiceNow%20CEO%20Bill%20McDermott%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EServiceNow%20reported%20strong%20Q1%202026%20results%2C%20raising%20forecasts%20amid%20AI%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Bill%20McDermott%20emphasized%20ServiceNow's%20AI%20product%20growth%20and%20dismissed%20AI%20competition%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EServiceNow's%20subscription%20revenue%20rose%2022%25%2C%20reaching%20%243.67%20billion%2C%20beating%20analysts'%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservicenow-ceo-buys-his-own-stock-commits-stay-2030-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EServiceNow%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20solid%20first-quarter%20results%20and%20raised%20forecasts%2C%20underscoring%20continued%20demand%20for%20its%20software%20even%20as%20questions%20swirl%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-executive-suggests-ai-agents-buy-software-licenses-seats-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20posted%20subscription%20revenue%20of%20%243.67%20billion%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20up%2022%25%20year%20over%20year.%20ServiceNow%20said%20it%20beat%20the%20high%20end%20of%20its%20guidance%20across%20all%20topline%20growth%20and%20profitability%20metrics%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20and%20lifted%20its%20full-year%20subscription%20revenue%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%202026%2C%20ServiceNow%20now%20expects%20subscription%20revenue%20of%20%2415.7%20billion%20to%20%2415.8%20billion%2C%20representing%20growth%20of%20roughly%2022%25%20to%2022.5%25.%20That%20beat%20Cowen%20analysts'%20expectations%20heading%20into%20the%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservicenow-ceo-bill-mc-dermott-ai-reorienting-global-economy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20McDermott%3C%2Fa%3E%20emphasized%20the%20company's%20momentum%20and%20once%20again%20dismissed%20the%20threat%20of%20AI%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20results%20speak%20a%20lot%20louder%20than%20the%20words.%20We're%20now%20in%20another%20beat%20and%20raised%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDermott%20highlighted%20accelerating%20adoption%20of%20ServiceNow's%20AI%20products%20as%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20growth.%20The%20company%20had%20previously%20forecast%20%241%20billion%20in%20AI%20software%20sales%20in%202026%2C%20and%20McDermott%20now%20expects%20that%20to%20be%20at%20least%20%241.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20probably%20blow%20through%20that%2C%20too%2C%20because%20the%20acceptance%20of%20our%20AI%20solutions%20is%20just%20absolutely%20stunning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20remaining%20performance%20obligations%2C%20a%20key%20forward-looking%20metric%2C%20rose%2025%25%20to%20%2427.7%20billion%2C%20while%20current%20RPO%20grew%2022.5%25%20to%20%2412.64%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoftware%20stocks%2C%20including%20ServiceNow%2C%20have%20been%20hammered%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%20on%20concerns%20that%20generative%20AI%20models%20and%20related%20offerings%20from%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-ate-world-now-ai-eating-software-saas-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereplace%20established%20software%20services.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDermott%20brushed%20those%20concerns%20aside%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20arguing%20instead%20that%20ServiceNow%20is%20benefiting%20from%20the%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20customers%20considering%20tapping%20AI%20models%20more%20directly%20are%20seeing%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20these%20new%20approaches%20can%20end%20up%20being%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20expected%2C%20due%20to%20unpredictable%20usage-based%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDermott%20said%20the%20CIO%20of%20a%20major%20customer%20recently%20evaluated%20a%20more%20direct%20AI%20model%20approach%20for%20running%20her%20IT%20operations.%20It%20would%20have%20cost%2010%20times%20more%20than%20just%20focusing%20on%20ServiceNow's%20AI%20offerings%2C%20which%20are%20more%20accurate%20and%20predictable%2C%20McDermott%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20AI%20model%20offerings%20for%20enterprise%20software%20customers%20%26quot%3Bparlor%20tricks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservicenow-ceo-dismisses-ai-thr